<h3><a href="#">Accommodation</a></h3>
<div>
<p>Some of your wedding party may wish to stay at Ardington House. We have nine double/twin rooms. Extra may be available on request. The House is available exclusively to the wedding family and rooms are available for personal preparation on the day.</p>
<p>We will also be happy to provide details of local hotels, inns and B &amp; B's in the area.</p>
<p>Milton Mill House Hotel 01235 831474 is a short drive away and can provide additional accommodation at preferential rates.</p>
